### [Psalms Chapter 36](../../../bib/kjv/psa036.htm#001.md)

Psalm 36. We have a needed warning as to the wicked, particularly the
enemies of righteousness, the instruments of Satan's power. There is no
conscience to be expected; nothing that will stop them in their evil
plans. The power and goodness of Jehovah are the sure refuge of those
that trust in Him. In result the wicked are cast down.

